description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Haunted & Hunted at Waverly Hills Edition

The boys are joined for a short visit with Shane Pittman of The Holzer Files and discuss Dave & Shane's recent adventure at Waverly Hills in Louisville, KY PLUS they share some BIG NEWS!  We also have stories of Bigfoot & Black Eyed Kids, Demi Lovato would date an alien, would you? An Alien Invasion is eminent and has begun by breaking up marriages! All this and MORE!

To get tix to see Dave & Shane visit: https://www.darknessradio.com/darknessdaveevents
